[I] A library providing Virtualization-based process isolation capabilities

[T] libkrun is a dynamic library that allows programs to easily acquire the
[T] ability to run processes in a partially isolated environment using KVM
[T] Virtualization on Linux and HVF on macOS/ARM64.

[U] https://github.com/containers/libkrun

[A] Sergio Lopez
[A] Jan Noha
[A] Matej Hrica
[A] Matias Ezequiel Vara Larsen
